CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,FA man who admitted severely injuring a
OL,7,Fpolice officer after he hit him with a
OL,8,Fcar in Dumfries has been jailed for
OL,9,Fmore than four years.
OL,11,FInspector Jonathan Edgar of Police
OL,12,FScotland was thrown across the road
OL,13,Fafter he was struck by the vehicle
OL,14,Fdriven by Martin McGroary on Herries
OL,15,FAvenue in Dumfries on 28 July 2025.
OL,17,FThe officer was left with a dislocated
OL,18,Fshoulder and head and facial injuries
OL,19,Fand has been unable to return to work.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,FMcGroary, 27, admitted driving in a
OL,7,F"culpable and reckless manner" and at
OL,8,F"excessive speed", and driving knowing
OL,9,Fthat Mr Edgar was on the road before
OL,10,Fthe collision when he appeared at the
OL,11,FHigh Court in Glasgow last month.
OL,13,FHe also pleaded guilty to failing to
OL,14,Fstop and give his details after the
OL,15,Fcollision and to driving without
OL,16,Finsurance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,FHe was jailed for four years and three
OL,7,Fmonths when he returned to the court
OL,8,Ffor sentencing on Thursday 27 May, and
OL,9,Fwas disqualified from driving for
OL,10,Fseven years.
OL,12,FMcGroary joined the hearing virtually
OL,13,Fon Thursday, 27 May.
OL,15,FSentencing him, Lord Cubie said: "You
OL,16,Fpleaded guilty to culpable and
OL,17,Freckless conduct.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,F"You are accepting a high degree of
OL,7,Frecklessness and acting with utter
OL,8,Fdisregard for the consequences of your
OL,9,Fconduct.
OL,11,F"I accept it was not your intention to
OL,12,Fendanger Inspector Edgar. I accept it
OL,13,Fwas a single act of recklessness where
OL,14,Fyou tried to escape from the scene and
OL,15,Fyou hit Inspector Edgar."
OL,17,FLord Cubie told him: "I recognise the
OL,18,Ftragic loss of your brother could have
OL,19,Faffected your thoughts and actions
OL,20,Fthat day."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,FAt a hearing last month, the court was
OL,7,Ftold police were called to the street
OL,8,Fshortly after midnight on 28 July by a
OL,9,Fresident who was concerned about the
OL,10,Fpresence of McGroary, whose brother
OL,11,Fhad recently died in a road crash.
OL,13,FSolicitor Advocate David Dickson KC,
OL,14,Fprosecuting, told the court that once
OL,15,Fpolice arrived, McGroary drove past Mr
OL,16,FEdgar, one of the officers present.
OL,18,FHe then continued driving towards the
OL,19,Fhouse before turning the car.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,FMr Dickson said officers then became
OL,7,F"concerned" that McGroary was going to
OL,8,Fget out of the car as it was the third
OL,9,Ftime he had driven up and down the
OL,10,Fstreet.
OL,12,FThe prosecutor said: "The accused
OL,13,Fclosed the driver door and was then
OL,14,Fseen accelerating, driving towards
OL,15,Fboth police vehicles and where
OL,16,FInspector Edgar stood beside the
OL,17,Fvehicle.
OL,19,F"In an effort to avoid being struck,
OL,20,Fhe began to run across the road
OL,21,Ftowards the pavement."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,FMr Dickson told the court that,
OL,7,Fdespite his efforts, the policeman was
OL,8,Fstruck by the car and was thrown about
OL,9,F10-15 feet across the road.
OL,11,FHe was taken to hospital where he was
OL,12,Ftreated for a dislocated shoulder and
OL,13,Fhead and facial injuries and was
OL,14,Fdischarged about 48 hours later.
OL,16,FJohn Scullion KC, defending, said on
OL,17,FThursday that McGroary, who is married
OL,18,Fand has four children, regrets what
OL,19,Fhappened.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,FHe said: "The incident giving rise to
OL,7,Fthe charge took place at a
OL,8,Fparticularly distressing time in his
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,F"In my submission it's clear he
OL,12,Faccepts full responsibility for his
OL,13,Factions. He displays remorse in
OL,14,Frelation to his behaviour and the
OL,15,Finjuries sustained by Mr Edgar."
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Scott Wilson said:
OL,18,F"This was a terrifying incident for
OL,19,Fthe officer involved, who was left
OL,20,Fwith serious injuries as a result of
OL,21,FMcGroary's actions.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1779977468
OL,3,CMan who hit police officer with car
OL,4,Cjailed for more than four years
OL,6,F"I hope this conviction brings some
OL,7,Fcomfort to the officer and his
OL,8,Fcolleagues and sends a message that
OL,9,Fthis type of violent behaviour against
OL,10,Fpolice officers and staff will not be
OL,11,Ftolerated."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/9
